  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK883">
<l>uṭpakai yañcittaṟ kākka vulaiviṭattu </l>
<l>maṭpakaiyiṉ māṇat teṟum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fear internal enmity and guard yourself; (if not) it will destroy (you) in an evil hour, as surely as the tool which cuts the potter's clay.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
